   { - 5} &amp; 5 &amp; 5  \cr 

 } } \right] \Rightarrow tr(A) = 1$$<br><br>Similarly,<br><br>$$B = {1 \over 5}(2(A + 2B) - (2A - B))$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 5}\left( {\left[ {\matrix{
   2 &amp; 4 &amp; 0  \cr 
   {12} &amp; { - 6} &amp; 6  \cr 
   { - 10} &amp; 6 &amp; 2  \cr 

 } } \right] - \left[ {\matrix{
